Class Review

java.lang.Object
com.FeedEmGreens.HealthyAura.entity.Review
@Entity public class Review extends Object
Entity representing a user-submitted review for an Eatery in the HealthyAura system.

Each Review record captures a user’s assessment of an eatery’s health and hygiene standards, textual feedback, and optional photo uploads. Reviews contribute to the platform’s transparency, user engagement, and recommendation scoring algorithms.

This entity also includes moderation metadata, allowing administrators to hide, delete, or review flagged submissions.

Entries are stored in the reviews table, with photo URLs stored in a separate review_photos collection table.

Example usage:

  • Users submit or update reviews for eateries
  • Admins moderate or hide inappropriate content
  • System awards points to users for eligible reviews
